# Trendora AI Recommendation & Search Backend

Production-ready AI backend powering the Trendora eCommerce app.

This system provides:

- Product search
- Personalized recommendations
- Learning-to-rank ranking
- Exploration vs exploitation
- Hybrid recommendation system
- Firebase product integration

---

# Architecture

Flutter App
↓
FastAPI Backend
↓
Search Pipeline
├ Elasticsearch Retrieval
├ Business Ranking
├ Learning-to-Rank (LightGBM)
├ Exploration (Bandit Strategy)
↓
Recommendation System
├ Content-Based Filtering
├ Top-K Similar Products
↓
Firebase Firestore (Product Storage)

---

# Features

## 1 Search System
- Elasticsearch BM25 search
- Query intent detection
- Price filters
- Category filters
- Sub-category filters
- Faceted search

Example endpoint:

GET /search?q=women shoes

---

## 2 Recommendation System

Content-based recommendation using product features.

Uses:

- TF-IDF embeddings
- cosine similarity
- Top-K similar products cache

Endpoint:

GET /recommendations?last_viewed_product_id=123

---

## 3 Similar Product Recommendation

Used on product detail page.

Endpoint:

GET /products/{product_id}/similar

---

## 4 Learning to Rank (LTR)

Ranking model trained with:

LightGBM Ranker

Features used:

- Elasticsearch relevance score
- Product popularity
- Average rating
- Discount

---

## 5 Exploration vs Exploitation

Multi-Armed Bandit system used to balance:

- best products
- new products
- diverse categories

---

## 6 Tracking System

User behavior logging for future ML training.

Endpoints:

POST /track/search  
POST /track/click  
POST /track/cart  

Stored in Firebase.

---

# API Endpoints

## Product APIs

GET /products  
GET /products/{product_id}

Used by Flutter to fetch product cards and details.

---

## Search API

GET /search

Example:

/search?q=men jackets&min_price=1000&max_price=5000

Supports:

- price filters
- category filters
- sub-category filters
- rating filters

---

## Recommendation APIs

GET /recommendations  
GET /products/{product_id}/similar

---

## Tracking APIs

POST /track/search  
POST /track/click  
POST /track/cart  

---


